Class Summary
SimpleExample A simple example that demonstrates the use of Jep for evaluation of a single expression.
 

Package com.singularsys.jepexamples Description

Container package for all examples.

  • com.singularsys.jepexamples.consoles Contain a set of console applications for interactive sessions using different configurations.
  • com.singularsys.jepexamples.applets contains some graphical applets using jep.
  • com.singularsys.jepexamples.diagnostics contains various applications for testing the performance of jep.
